title: Deeplink with app terminated - Auto
custom_steps:
1. Open At Bat
2. Force Quit
3. Launch Safari
4. Enter deeplink URL: mlbatbat://team?team_id=111
5. Accept system dialog for opening page in At Bat
custom_expected: Opens team page for Boston Red Sox

title: Deeplink with app backgrounded - Auto
custom_steps:
1. Open At Bat
2. Tap home button to background the app
3. Launch Safari
4. Enter deeplink URL: mlbatbat://team?team_id=111
5. Accept system dialog for opening page in At Bat
custom_expected: Opens team page for Boston Red Sox

title: Deeplink with modal open and app backgrounded - Auto
custom_steps:
1. Open At Bat
2. Navigate to the News section and click the first article
3. Press home button to background app
4. Launch Safari
5. Enter deeplink URL: mlbatbat://team?team_id=111
6. Accept system dialog for opening page in At Bat
custom_expected: Opens team page for Boston Red Sox

title: Deeplink with a favorite team set and app backgrounded - Auto
custom_steps:
1. Open At Bat
2. Navigate to favorite teams picker screen and select the Red Sox as the favorite team
3. Tap home button to background the app
4. Launch Safari
5. Enter deeplink URL: mlbatbat://team?team_id=111
6. Accept system dialog for opening page in At Bat
custom_expected: Opens team page for Boston Red Sox where you can change tabs and teams.
